edBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T11:44:10.000Z","msg":"預計到將會痛苦已經是最大的痛苦，那根本等於絕望。<br />\n不過如果不要將自己看得那麼重，來這個世界為的就是這個世界而不是為自己，就自然不會有要不要自殺這個問題。<br />\n古人的目光很多時都是放在這個宇宙之上，現代人目光很多時就只由自己的左手到自己的右手。不要說家事國事天下事事事關心了，連自己身邊的事都唔關心，那當然只在乎自己生而為人的荒謬。"},{"pid":"4b5bbeef362ff7cd82c998c09af0cd69e193d716","tid":2293508,"uid":286206,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"34c1e6fc1699d494756ba9139650960e7896de12","tid":2293508,"uid":125219,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a470e9a315175b69540ecaffcb806d70fb3266d5","tid":2293508,"uid":286206,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5892accb782189ca3c9667d5373e087aa7fe6794","tid":2293508,"uid":50060,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T11:26:31.000Z","msg":"點解要自殺？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T11:37:37.000Z","msg":"生不如死"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T11:40:09.000Z","msg":"點樣生不如死法？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T11:44:14.000Z","msg":"每個人把尺都唔同 點講比你知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我只係簡化Shelly Kagan一大篇野幾十頁得出結論就係生不如死自殺可以係理性選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8f7ae834516b774cc72faf2696e4d4aeb605e4e","tid":2293508,"uid":47901,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T11:58:31.000Z","msg":"人的世界，必無完美，只有缺陷，因此痛苦與人同在，幼少孩童可例外<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2179468\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2179468</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5c78609edf85d98dbce366eedfaf1aa6a391c59b","tid":2293508,"uid":47901,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e8f7ae834516b774cc72faf2696e4d4aeb605e4e","tid":2293508,"uid":47901,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T11:58:31.000Z","msg":"人的世界，必無完美，只有缺陷，因此痛苦與人同在，幼少孩童可例外<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2179468\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2179468</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T11:59:33.000Z","msg":"人生＝同無窮盡的缺陷苦鬥至死"},{"pid":"52e4